<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> als von geleits wegen
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat,
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>. Nu als uns
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> nehst mitsampt den
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den kürfürsten auch von
                                <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geleits wegen
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, in
                                <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief begriffen was, daz wir
                        darümb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedigen
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>margr<ex>af</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Brandb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc. von
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> aller wegen
                            <expan>antwurte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>solte<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        desmals <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>benante<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>margr<ex>af</ex></expan> von ewr aller wegen
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>besigelte<ex>n</ex></expan> offen geleitsbrief
                            <expan>gegeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>,
                        als wir nu on czweyfel sein, daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der <expan>margr<ex>af</ex></expan> dasselbig,
                        ee <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden diser <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        brief <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> werde, eygentlich verkündiget und
                        czu wissen getan hab. Und wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>furstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> gnaden lieb und dinst beweisen möchten
                        etc. <expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>eria</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Margaret<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>virg<ex>inis</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
